name: Peculiar Weather
description:
Music & Artwork by Sennóide
Title: Peculiar Weather

Audio File: MP3 320 kbps
Duration: 01:56
File Size: 4,6 MB
Audio channels: Stereo

The music describes a scene where two men are preparing for a secret operation in CAIRO some time during the early 1900's. However, one of them tried some hashish he acquired from one of the locals and seems to be more concerned with the peculiar weather in EGYPT than the mission at hand...
